ory":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/OFO69/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/knife-io/embed?sid=1","plays":41729,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"}}],["$","$L5","O5W86",{"game":{"id":"O5W86","slug":"jigsaw-collections","title":"Jigsaw Collections","description":"Jigsaw puzzle is one of the entertaining, educational games that requires perseverance, accuracy, patience, and most importantly - to be attentive to the little things. Online jigsaw puzzles always attract a huge audience of completely different ages. In our game, everyone can find interesting collections for themselves! A game of this kind is an intrigue, a mystery that both an adult and a child would like to unravel. Search and combine the pieces into a single picture. For convenience, you can zoom in or out on the work surface. We wish you only victories!","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["puzzles"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/O5W86/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/jigsaw-collections/embed?sid=1","plays":41323,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"}}],["$","$L5","U6AL0",{"game":{"id":"U6AL0","slug":"neon-king-a-local-multiplayer-platformer","title":"Neon King - A local multiplayer Platformer","description":"Neon King est un jeu de canapé multijoueur local\n\n dans lequel ton seul but est\n\n pour éliminer votre adversaire.","category":"Multijoueur","tags":["arcade"],"thumbnail":"https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U6AL0/thumbnail/small.png","url":"https://play.gamepix.com/neon-king-a-local-multiplayer-platformer/embed?sid=1","plays":40782,"rating":4.7,"featured":false,"source":"gamepix"}}]]}]]}]]}]]}]}]]],null],null]},["$","$L6",null,{"parallelRouterKey":"children","segmentPath":["children","game","children","$7","children"],"error":"$undefined","errorStyles":"$undefined","errorScripts":"$undefined","template":["$","$L8",null,{}],"templateStyles":"$undefined","templateScripts":"$und